ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of HEATHER KENNEDY of Calgary, Alberta, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 13, 2018, in the place of David James Cohen, whose term will expire.
